Title : John Rochon
Text : '''John Rochon''' is a [[Canadians|Canadian]] shooter.

He won bronze for [[Canada]] in [[1998 Commonwealth Games]]. He is the oldest person to represent Canada in the [[Commonwealth Games]], when he was aged 65.<ref>http://www.commonwealthgames.ca/team-canada/games/commonwealth-games.html</ref>

He was awarded [[List of members of the Order of Ontario|the Order of Ontario]] in 2004.

